title: Do you think PancakeSwap should have DeFi insurance to protect users' funds and refund them in case of loss or hacker attack?
body: Some DeFi platforms were hacked a while ago and many people lost their funds. Through this vote, we can show PancakeSwap that it can do differently and be a much safer platform for its users. We in the community want to continue to trust PancakeSwap and all its services, so we invite everyone to vote in favor of protecting their money invested in the platform.
author: 0x72599a782Cf0a4a94d16F91Bd9Eb26192e110867
